    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/1bceb13f26a626ef217ec679a6252875.avif?t=1726378663\" width=256 height=100 /></span><br><br><strong>跑步、跳跃、用长矛攻击动物并收集肉。<br>利用各种道具来帮助狩猎，让饥饿的原始人不再饥饿，这取决于你们。<br>准备好和饥饿的原始人一起展开新生代冒险了吗？</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特征</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/00972f63ff12252c99749ef7b2d74f90.poster.avif?t=1726378663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/00972f63ff12252c99749ef7b2d74f90.webm?t=1726378663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/00972f63ff12252c99749ef7b2d74f90.mp4?t=1726378663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>[[list]<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 简单但精巧的狩猎系统</li></ul>完美的速度和角度对于原始人的完美狩猎至关重要。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/ca23aee355d1af6f90a3e2136de95083.poster.avif?t=1726378663\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/ca23aee355d1af6f90a3e2136de95083.webm?t=1726378663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/ca23aee355d1af6f90a3e2136de95083.mp4?t=1726378663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 具有多种效果的武器</li></ul>有3种武器具有特殊能力帮助原始人打猎。<br>利用特殊武器打猎吧！<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 拥有多种效果的被动能力</li></ul>原始人可以在你们的帮助下获得狩猎所需的能力。<br>可以记住以前的速度和以前的角度，还可以检测猎物的位置！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/fc9759bb4547ee8122fd008f348ecd75.poster.avif?t=1726378663\" width=330 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/fc9759bb4547ee8122fd008f348ecd75.webm?t=1726378663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/fc9759bb4547ee8122fd008f348ecd75.mp4?t=1726378663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>[清单] <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 在5个地区狩猎的10种以上的动物 [/清单]<br>各地可以猎取各种动物。<br>感受一下新生代时代的现场感吧。</li></ul>",
